      "rationale": "Testing was conducted at a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending load condition. While the protocol is standardized and well-controlled, only one test condition was evaluated. This limits the ability to bound model behavior across the full COU response space, resulting in an achieved level of 2 against a required level of 3. This gap is acknowledged and documented as an identified limitation of the validation campaign."
