      "rationale": "Across all three FEA ensemble members and all three QoIs, percent differences between simulation and experimental mean were below 8.4%, and the E/uval metric remained below 1.96. Both pre-established acceptance criteria are satisfied, supporting a Gradation 3 output comparison assessment."
